snippet.title: Amber Rose discusses life with Kanye West and more.
snippet.description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with Amber Rose. They discuss Amber's love of hip hop, her life before the spotlight, her work with 'Slut Walk' and a lot more. In this clip Amber Rose discusses life with Kanye West and more. Watch the full video here:
